code: /**  * Description of test.  *  * @throws Exception in the event of a test error.  */ @Test public void testConstructorOne() throws Exception {     instance = new MllpSocketException(TEST_EXCEPTION_MESSAGE).     assertNull(instance.getCause()).     assertEquals(TEST_EXCEPTION_MESSAGE, instance.getMessage()). }
